cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image analysis and segmentation. The use of deep learning algorithms also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The paper also involves point label encoding methods, which could suggest it belongs to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) category. Finally, the application of the algorithm on stained tissue images suggests it could belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
